      "id": "e38dc563f4c958a9",
      "text": "If before we believed that successful seeking is an action that we can simply will through, now we may experience the thought that crosses to it:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "462d8e23480ad1dd",
      "text": "Successful search does not become successful by searching, but by letting ourselves be found by the solution."
    },
